casebody.data:
Philip Milligan, Respondent v. The Metropolitan Elevated Railway Company, et al., Appellants. Decided January 11, 1892. Appeal by defendants from judgment entered upon report of referee. Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. Edwin M. Felt, for respondent.

Before Freedman, P. J., McAdam and Gilder-sleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
